description:
Sonic Underground: Christmas Tree Special Summary:
When Bartleby, his lover Sonic, and the rest of the hedgehog family head to walmart in search of the perfect Christmas tree, struggles of Bartleby's childhood begin to come to light. Sonic will do everything he can to give Bartleby the Christmas that he never had as a child

Run time - 20 minutes

Starring:
Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin
Sonic the Hedgehog
Manic the Hedgehog
Sonia the Hedgehog
Knuckles the Echidna
Queen Aleena
Uncle Chuck
Sir Montclair(Bartleby's father)
